# Base URL of the backend API (include the /api suffix).
# Leave unset to use the built-in defaults:
#   - dev build   -> http://localhost:5000/api
#   - prod build  -> https://car-dealership-inventory-system-vl4p.onrender.com/api
# Set this to override (e.g. on Vercel):
